### Results:

Ō£ģ **Single-Step Process**: Immediate polyline appears after first point placement
Ō£ģ **Floating Done Button**: Semi-transparent green button appears in top-right immediately after first point
Ō£ģ **Dynamic Polyline**: White line with distance label follows mouse movement (like Google Maps)
Ō£ģ **Real-Time Updates**: Distance updates instantly as user moves mouse over map
Ō£ģ **Improved UX**: More intuitive flow similar to Google Maps measurement tool
Ō£ģ **Clean State Management**: Proper cleanup of temporary elements and event listeners
