- **Limited Visibility**: Only showed current format in tooltip

### Solution Applied:

**Replaced Gear Icon with Dropdown Selector**:

```tsx
// Before (gear icon cycling)
<Button
  size="sm"
  variant="ghost"
  onClick={() =>
    setCurrentFormatIndex(
      (prev) => (prev + 1) % formatDisplays.length
    )
  }
  className="h-6 w-6 p-0"
  title={`Coordinate format: ${formatDisplays[currentFormatIndex].label}`}
>
  <Settings className="w-3 h-3" />
</Button>

// After (dropdown selector)
<Select
  value={currentFormatIndex.toString()}
  onValueChange={(value) => setCurrentFormatIndex(parseInt(value))}
>
  <SelectTrigger className="h-6 w-auto min-w-[120px] text-xs">
    <SelectValue />
  </SelectTrigger>
  <SelectContent>
    {formatDisplays.map((format, index) => (
      <SelectItem key={format.key} value={index.toString()}>
        {format.label}
      </SelectItem>
    ))}
  </SelectContent>
</Select>
```

### Results:

