Ō£ģ **Desktop Maintained**: Single-line layout preserved for tablet/desktop (md: breakpoint)  
Ō£ģ **Button Wrapping**: Action buttons wrap naturally on mobile without overflow  
Ō£ģ **Clean Layout**: Route name gets full width, buttons stack below on mobile  
Ō£ģ **No Layout Issues**: Eliminates mobile overflow problems

### Features Implemented:

