**Z-Index Conflict**:

- **AppBar**: `z-30` (higher priority)
- **Waypoints Trigger**: `z-20` (lower priority)
- **Result**: AppBar covers waypoints button on mobile devices

**Positioning Issue**: Waypoints trigger at `top-20` was too close to AppBar at `top-3`

### Solution Applied:

**1. Ō£ģ Increased Z-Index**:

```tsx
// Before: Lower z-index than AppBar
<div className="absolute top-20 left-3 z-20 flex items-center gap-2 lg:hidden">

// After: Higher z-index than AppBar
<div className="absolute top-24 left-3 z-40 flex items-center gap-2 lg:hidden">
```

**2. Ō£ģ Dynamic AppBar Height Measurement + Safe-Area Aware Positioning**:

```tsx
// Before: Brittle marginTop positioning
<div className="absolute left-3 z-50 flex items-center gap-2 lg:right-3 lg:left-auto" style={{ top: "calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + 96px)" }}>

// After: Dynamic positioning based on measured AppBar height
<div className="absolute left-3 z-20 flex items-center gap-2 lg:right-3 lg:left-auto" style={{ top: `calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + ${appBarH + 8}px)` }}>
```

**3. Ō£ģ Fixed "Add at crosshair" Button**:

```tsx
