**5. Ō£ģ Enhanced Button Positioning with Safety Floor and ResizeObserver**:

```tsx
// Before: Basic dynamic positioning
style={{ top: `calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + ${appBarH + 20}px)` }}

// After: Safety floor + higher z-index for resilience
style={{
  top: `max(calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + ${appBarH + 20}px), 120px)`,
}}
className="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-40 flex justify-center"
```

**6. Ō£ģ Reactive AppBar Height Measurement**:

```tsx
// Before: Basic resize listener
useEffect(() => {
  const read = () => {
    /* ... */
  };
  read();
  window.addEventListener("resize", read);
  return () => window.removeEventListener("resize", read);
}, []);

// After: ResizeObserver + resize listener for complete coverage
useEffect(() => {
  if (!appBarRef.current) return;

  const read = () =>
    setAppBarH(appBarRef.current!.getBoundingClientRect().height);
  read();

  const ro = new ResizeObserver(read);
  ro.observe(appBarRef.current);

  const onResize = () => read();
  window.addEventListener("resize", onResize);

  return () => {
    ro.disconnect();
    window.removeEventListener("resize", onResize);
  };
}, []);
```

**7. Ō£ģ Enhanced Waypoints Positioning with Safety Floor**:

```tsx
// Before: Basic dynamic positioning
style={{ top: `calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + ${appBarH + 8}px)` }}

// After: Safety floor + increased spacing
style={{
  top: `max(calc(env(safe-area-inset-top) + ${appBarH + 12}px), 96px)`,
}}
```

