**Solution Applied**:

- **Standalone Disclaimer Page**: `/disclaimer` with full legal text and SEO metadata
- **Footer Integration**: Added disclaimer link to site-wide footer
- **First-Use Modal**: Non-blocking disclaimer modal in route builder (shows once per device)
- **SEO Optimization**: Added to sitemap and structured data

