## Task: Fix Distance Units & Add Polyline Click to Insert Waypoints

### Issues Reported:

1. **Label glitchiness**: Labels were still flickering during interactions
2. **Inconsistent units**: Route distance shown in km while speed is in knots
3. **Missing feature**: No way to insert waypoints between existing legs

### Solutions Implemented:

**1. Ō£ģ Fixed Distance Units (km ŌåÆ nautical miles)**:

```tsx
// Before (in lib/route-utils.ts)
export function formatDistance(meters: number): string {
  if (meters < 1000) {
    return `${Math.round(meters)} m`;
  } else if (meters < 10000) {
    return `${(meters / 1000).toFixed(1)} km`;
  } else {
    return `${Math.round(meters / 1000)} km`;
  }
}

// After
export function formatDistance(meters: number): string {
  const nauticalMiles = meters / 1852;
  if (nauticalMiles < 0.1) {
    return `${Math.round(meters)} m`;
  } else if (nauticalMiles < 10) {
    return `${nauticalMiles.toFixed(1)} nm`;
  } else {
    return `${Math.round(nauticalMiles)} nm`;
  }
}
```

**2. Ō£ģ Improved Label Debouncing**:

- Increased debounce time from 150ms to 250ms for smoother label updates
- Reduces flickering during zoom and other operations

**3. Ō£ģ Click-to-Insert Waypoints**:

```tsx
// Added click listeners to polylines
polyline.addListener("click", (event: google.maps.PolyMouseEvent) => {
  if (event.latLng) {
    const clickedPosition = {
      lat: event.latLng.lat(),
      lng: event.latLng.lng(),
    };
    
    // Insert waypoint between start and end
    insertWaypointAtIndex(i + 1, clickedPosition);
  }
});

// New function to insert at specific index
const insertWaypointAtIndex = useCallback(
  (index: number, coordinates: Coordinates) => {
    setWaypoints((prev) => {
      saveToUndoStack(prev);
      
      const wp: Waypoint = {
        id: generateWaypointId(),
        name: generateWaypointName(prev.length),
        coordinates,
        timestamp: Date.now(),
      };
      
      // Insert at the specified index
      const next = [...prev.slice(0, index), wp, ...prev.slice(index)];
      
      fetchElevationForWaypoint(wp.id, wp.coordinates);
      setHasUnsavedChanges(true);
      
      return next;
    });
  },
  [setWaypoints]
);
```

**4. Ō£ģ Visual Hover Feedback**:

```tsx
// Polylines lighten and thicken on hover to indicate clickability
polyline.addListener("mouseover", () => {
  polyline.setOptions({
    strokeColor: "#60a5fa", // Lighter blue
    strokeWeight: 4,         // Thicker
  });
});

polyline.addListener("mouseout", () => {
  polyline.setOptions({
    strokeColor: "#3b82f6", // Original blue
    strokeWeight: 3,
  });
});
```

### Results:

Ō£ģ **Consistent Units**: All distances now in nautical miles (nm) to match knots
Ō£ģ **Smoother Labels**: Increased debounce reduces flickering
Ō£ģ **Flexible Route Building**: Click any route leg to insert waypoint at that position
Ō£ģ **Visual Feedback**: Polylines highlight on hover to show they're clickable
Ō£ģ **Undo Support**: All waypoint insertions are tracked in undo stack

