- ­¤æü’ĖÅ **Visual Cues**: Hover effect shows where you can click to insert
- ­¤Ä» **Precise Positioning**: Insert waypoint exactly where you need it on the route
- ­¤öä **Undo-Friendly**: All insertions can be undone

